elements.name: Verify accepting and ignoring a connection request

steps.name: I login with user from Excel
user navigates to My Network section
user opens the Received Invitations list
user captures screenshot of received requests
user clicks on Accept for the first request
user scrolls down till last request
user clicks on Ignore for the last request
